<subSubSection pageId="6" pageNumber="203" type="biology_ecology">
<paragraph blockId="6.[151,1127,727,1104]" pageId="6" pageNumber="203">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,243,727,751]" pageId="6" pageNumber="203">Biology.</emphasis>
Adults: wingspan 
<quantity box="[444,559,728,752]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.85" metricValueMax="1.9" metricValueMin="1.8" pageId="6" pageNumber="203" unit="mm" value="18.5" valueMax="19.0" valueMin="18.0">18-19 mm</quantity>
. In north-eastern 
<collectingRegion box="[746,808,727,751]" country="Italy" name="Sicilia" pageId="6" pageNumber="203">Sicily</collectingRegion>
the species flies from June to September and can be observed up to ca. 
<quantity box="[595,683,760,784]" metricMagnitude="0" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.2" pageId="6" pageNumber="203" unit="m" value="1.2">1,200 m</quantity>
a.s.l. It flies at dusk, together with 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Schawerda" authorityYear="1933" class="Insecta" family="Pterophoridae" genus="Stenoptilia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="203" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="grisescens">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="203">S. grisescens</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, hiding in grass if disturbed; some specimens were collected at a light trap. Larval host plant: probably monophagous on 
<taxonomicName box="[561,717,825,848]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Plantaginaceae" genus="Kickxia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="6" pageNumber="203" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="spuria">
<emphasis box="[561,717,825,848]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="203">Kickxia spuria</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(L.) Dumort. (
<taxonomicName box="[875,1065,823,847]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Scrophulariaceae" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="6" pageNumber="203" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="family">Scrophulariaceae</taxonomicName>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="6.[151,1127,727,1104]" box="[151,866,855,880]" pageId="6" pageNumber="203">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,252,855,880]" pageId="6" pageNumber="203">Range in</emphasis>
